high_descs: Go left and then right and then turn right to face the tomato on the round table.
Pick the bread up from the table.
Go around the table and go forward and turn left to face the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge and shut the door, open the door and take the bread out.
Go left and the right and stand in front of the round table.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go straight back and then right to find the round table.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the left side of the table.
Carry the bread and turn right, then left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door, then open it again and take the bread out. Shut the door.
Carry the bread and turn left, then right to go back to the table.
Place the bread on the far left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the window. Turn left and go to the table.
Pick up the loaf of bread beside the wine bottle.
Turn right and walk towards the window. Turn left and walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the bread inside the refrigerator next to the egg and shut the door. Wait 5 seconds, open the refrigerator door and remove the bread.
Turn left and walk towards the window. Turn right and go to the table. Turn right.
Place bread on the table next to the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Chill bread in the refrigerator and return it to the table.
